PR4.F.summary: Protector Forsikring ASA, a general insurance company, provides various insurance products to the commercial and public sectors, and the affinity insurance markets in Norway, Sweden, Denmark, the United Kingdom, and Finland. The company sells its products to non-marine industries through insurance brokers, and real estate agents and lawyers. Protector Forsikring ASA was founded in 2003 and is based in Oslo, Norway.
